3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 스프링 mvc request life cycle</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 84%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"/static/4b5494eb8451df532e76955784aeb78e/fcda8/mvclifecycle.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4b5494eb8451df532e76955784aeb78e/5a46d/mvclifecycle.png 300w,\n/static/4b5494eb8451df532e76955784aeb78e/fcda8/mvclifecycle.png 590w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"2-filter와-interceptor는-실행-시점이-다르다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-filter%EC%99%80-interceptor%EB%8A%94-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89-%EC%8B%9C%EC%A0%90%EC%9D%B4-%EB%8B%A4%EB%A5%B4%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"2 filter와 interceptor는 실행 시점이 다르다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Filter와 Interceptor는 실행 시점이 다르다.</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Filter는 WebApplication에 등록 - web.xml</li>\n<li>Interceptor는 Spring의 Context에 등록</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"3-interceptor와-filter의-차이\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-interceptor%EC%99%80-filter%EC%9D%98-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4\" aria-label=\"3 interceptor와 filter의 차이 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Interceptor와 Filter의 차이</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Interceptor는 시큐리티가 나오기전에 인증, 권한을 체크하는 훌륭한 도구로 사용되었다.</li>\n<li>Interceptor는 AOP를 흉내낼 수 있다. handlerMethod를 제공하기 때문에 메서드의 전후 처리가 가능하다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"4-security\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-security\" aria-label=\"4 security permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. Security</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Security의 인증 절차는 필터 체인을 거쳐 dispatcherservlet으로 가기전에 적용된다.</li>\n<li>그리고 Security는 필터 체인을 통해서 걸러진 request 요청을 Interceptor를 이용해서 전후 처리할 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"5-security-인증-절차\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-security-%EC%9D%B8%EC%A6%9D-%EC%A0%88%EC%B0%A8\" aria-label=\"5 security 인증 절차 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. Security 인증 절차</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Security를 통한 로그인은 Authentication 객체의 모험(여행)이라고 생각하면 이해하기 쉽다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>시큐리티가 로그인 하는 과정을 직접 해보는 예제하기</p>\n<h2 id=\"6-스프링-시큐리티-설정-파일-참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-%EC%8A%A4%ED%94%84%EB%A7%81-%EC%8B%9C%ED%81%90%EB%A6%AC%ED%8B%B0-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"6 스프링 시큐리티 설정 파일 참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. 스프링 시큐리티 설정 파일 참고</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://bamdule.tistory.com/53\">https://bamdule.tistory.com/53</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"springboot 블로그 12.시큐리티 동작 원리","date":"November 07, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/spring/blog/blog-12/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/spring/security/basic-1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"springboot security 1. 스프링부트 시큐리티 환경설정"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/spring/security/basic-2/"},"frontmatter":{